Class HttpSpace

java.lang.Object
io.nosqlbench.adapters.api.activityimpl.uniform.BaseSpace<HttpSpace>
io.nosqlbench.adapter.http.core.HttpSpace
All Implemented Interfaces:
Space, NBNamedElement, NBLabeledElement, AutoCloseable
public class HttpSpace extends BaseSpace<HttpSpace> implements NBLabeledElement
ThreadLocal http clients have been removed from this version, as the built-in HTTP client implementation is meant to be immutable. If shared-state issues occur, thread-local support will be re-added.
